# Private operator notes — NOT for public GitBook.
# Reasons:
#   client01.md       contains demo passwords (admin1234 / demo1234)
#   ops_metrics.md    contains SSH key paths + EC2 IPs + RDS internal hostname
#   SECRETS.md        filename alone is a red flag; superseded by docs/security/secret-management.md
#   docs/quickstart.md  superseded by docs/introduction/quickstart.md
#   docs/runbooks/    superseded by docs/operations/runbooks/
#   CLIENT.md         operator/customer walkthrough — contains demo password admin1234
docs/client01.md
docs/ops_metrics.md
docs/SECRETS.md
docs/quickstart.md
docs/runbooks/
CLIENT.md

# ==========================================
# Session audit + ops artifacts
# ==========================================
# Anything generated under audit_*/, FIXES_*.md, or similar one-shot session
# dirs is *operational evidence*, not product source. These often contain
# OpenAPI dumps, probe results, hit counts, JWT lengths, demo passwords,
# and account ids — fine for the operator's working tree, NOT for git.
audit_*/
FIXES_APPLIED.md
HONEST_STATUS_*.md
DEPLOY_REPORT_*.md
SPRINT_*_REPORT.md
SOAK_REPORT_*.md
session_*/
reports/
brutal_*.md
debug_*.txt

# ==========================================
# AWS / cloud one-off credential files
# Sprint A8 — defensive: catch every common .env.* shape so a future
# .env.aws.staging / .env.aws.prod / .env.ci.local can't slip past
# the per-folder .gitignore in voice-agent/.
# ==========================================
**/.env.aws*
**/.env.ci*
**/.env.staging*
**/.env.prod*
**/.env.production*
**/.env.dev*
**/.env.test*
**/.env.local*
**/aws_credentials
**/.aws/credentials
**/.aws/config

# ==========================================
# Secrets toolchain — never commit a real .pypirc / .npmrc with tokens
# ==========================================
.pypirc
**/.pypirc
.npmrc
**/.npmrc
.gem/credentials

# ==========================================
# Audit + verification helpers that leave creds on disk
# ==========================================
/tmp/aegis_token
/tmp/aegis_apikey
*aegis_token*
*aegis_apikey*
*aegis_jwt*

